parameters:
Wow! It's amazing! You're quite fast...! You're doing great with
Suisui-chan...!

Heheh! Because I have a top-notch engine installed! I won't be a
match for any ordinary ship around here!
I-I'm a little...! It's too fast, it's scary...!!

It's just a matter of getting used to it, Laura-san! Please keep
up with the speed of Suisui-chan!!
I-I understand...! I-I need to become faster...!
Huh? You don't seem energetic. Is something wrong?

How should I put it... I'm not really good with this swaying
feeling... It's a bit nauseating, you know...

Ah, so this is what they call motion sickness. Yep, yep, it's a
sign of youth, huh.
Suisui-chan... It's amazing! I wish it could go even faster!
We can go! This is twice as fast as the maximum speed!
It can go twice as fast...!? I definitely want to see that speed!

If you're expecting that much, I can't refuse...! Activating Full
Speed Suisui-chan...!!
What speed...!? No, this is addictive...!!
H-hi...hi...!!! I can't...I can't keep up with this...!?
Laura, look! It's so fast that I can't see anything...!
Impossible...!! It's scary!! I don't want to see it...!!
Sigh... It's just like playing with a child's toy...
Ah, this is our destination. We will get off here.
Huh? There's no ladder or anything.

Dive in the direction of 3 o'clock from here! We can infiltrate
by utilizing the opening and closing of the floodgate!
Well, this is where we part ways. Everyone, take care.

Same goes for you. Well, with that gorilla around, we'll manage
somehow.

...Hmm. Without me, your fighting power will be significantly
reduced, but do your best over there too.
Huh? Wait, I haven't been called gorilla just now...?
Maybe it's just my imagination... Haha...
